name: Franklin Roosevelt Square, São Paulo
description: Stitched panorama showing a neat grouping of buildings next to a square in the city's theater district. This square, not pictured, is a Brutalist concrete platform built on top of a huge and busy freeway that traverses the city center. Location: -23.548552, -46.646621. Originally released as HeN OBJKT 114340 on 4 June 2021.
